                            |
                            | Coventry Farms offers lessons for beginners all the way up through the Grand Prix level, on seasoned bomb-proof horses.  Expert hunter/jumper training is available for both human and equine athletes wishing to compete at the local and national level.  Clients benefit from the McConnell's decades of experience and an environment that is conducive to education and performance at the top levels of hunter/jumper competition.
                            |
                            | Contact us today for more information regarding lessons, boarding, and sales.
                        a.btn.btn-light.btn-xl(href='#services') Our services

        // Services
        section#services.page-section
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                h2.text-center.mt-0 Coventry Farms Services
