                            p.text-muted.mb-0 Board prices include feeding, watering, and the cleaning of stalls. (prices here)
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-laptop.fs-1.text-primary
